member.example:
This sample shows how to call AddOperationAsync.

Uri endpoint = new Uri("<https://my-service.azure.com>");
ResiliencyServiceDrivenClient client = new ResiliencyServiceDrivenClient(endpoint, "<serviceDeploymentVersion>");

Response response = await client.AddOperationAsync();

Console.WriteLine(response.Status);

